Question: One image shows a man behind and holding on to two hitched oxen who are running and creating splashes of water.

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a man behind and holding on to two hitched oxen?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a man behind and holding on to two hitched oxen?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the oxen running and creating splashes of water?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the oxen running and creating splashes of water?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
